
===================================
📌 1. Finglish Version (Persian Latin Script)
===================================

📖 **Tashrih:**
    `bashbug` yek dastoor nist ke be soorat pishfarz dar distro-haye Linux ya Unix vojud dashte bashe. Ehtemalan yek dastoor ya script-e khosoosi hast ke shoma sakhteed ya download kardeed. Baraye etela'at bishtar, bayad manba' ya code-e asli-e aan ra bebinid. Dar kol, agar yek dastoor ya script bash bashad, baraye anjam-e amali khass neveshte shode ast.

⚙️ **Gozine-ha:**
    Chun `bashbug` yek dastoor standard nist, gozine-haye khas-i nadarad magar inke dar script-e asli tarif shode bashand. Agar script ra khodetan neveshte-id, mitavanid gozine-ha ra ba estefade az `getopts` daroon-e script tarif konid. Dar gheir in surat, bayad code-e script ra check konid ta az gozine-haye dastres motale' shavid.

🛠 **Mesal-ha:**

    $ bashbug  
    🔹 Run kardan script ya dastoor `bashbug` ba estefade az gozine-haye pishfarz (agar tarif shode bashand).

    $ bashbug --help
    🔹 Ehtemalan namayesh rahnamayi baraye dastoor agar `--help` dar script tarif shode bashad.

✅ **Mesal sade:**

    $ ./bashbug
    🔹  Run kardan script `bashbug` az rahe directory-e jari. Agar `bashbug` executable nabashad, bayad dastoor `chmod +x bashbug` ra ghablan ejra konid.

